{"type":"text","timestamp":1775865471634,"sessionID":"ses_2863226e8ffepDL9AgHZo0O2a1","part":{"id":"prt_d79d48ea5001gx1kDu46vBDSqt","messageID":"msg_d79d48385001tfVdKbiq1yl7fB","sessionID":"ses_2863226e8ffepDL9AgHZo0O2a1","type":"text","text":"Implementation of AR-024 — DockerService封装 is complete.\n\n**Summary of changes:**\n\n1. **DockerService** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`):\n   - Added `_format_size(size_bytes)` - formats bytes to KB/MB/GB\n   - Added `_get_image_info(image_name)` - internal method with size formatting\n   - Added `_docker_login_sdk(registry, username, password)` - Docker registry authentication\n   - Added `_tag_image_sdk(source_image, target_image)` - image tagging\n   - Updated `build_image` return to include `image_name`, `image_id`, `image_size`, `build_time`\n   - Updated `get_image_info` return to include `created` field\n   - Updated `push_image` return to include `pushed_image`, `push_time` and handle retagging\n   - Added generic Exception catch as fallback\n   - Updated `remove_image` to return False for non-existent images with warning\n\n2. **PackRuntime** (`agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`):\n   - Added Docker availability check when `build_mode == \"local\"`\n   - Raises `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")` if unavailable\n\n3. **PublishRuntime** (`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`):\n   - Added DockerService integration\n   - Added `_prepare_local_image()` method for pushing images to registry\n\n4. **Unit Tests** (`tests/test_docker_service.py`):\n   - Added 26 comprehensive unit tests covering all new functionality\n\nAll 125 tests pass.","time":{"start":1775865471633,"end":1775865471633}}}
